Interface BulkExecutor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AsyncBulkExecutor, AsyncBulkReader, AsyncBulkWriter, AutoCloseable, BulkReader, BulkWriter, ReactiveBulkExecutor, ReactiveBulkReader, ReactiveBulkWriter, SyncBulkExecutor, SyncBulkReader, SyncBulkWriter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReactorBulkExecutor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBulkExecutor, ContinuousReactorBulkExecutor, DefaultReactorBulkExecutor

    public interface BulkExecutor
extends BulkWriter, BulkReader, SyncBulkExecutor, AsyncBulkExecutor, ReactiveBulkExecutor
    An execution unit for bulk writes and bulk reads that operates in 3 distinct modes: synchronous (blocking), asynchronous (non-blocking), and reactive.
